<L>__{interior duct day}
<A>__{in the duct, ethan signals to krieger, making a triangle of his hands. krieger wriggles forward and hands him a multi sided, pyramid shaped glass object. ethan raises the pyramid and intercepts a portion of one of the laser net's beams. the pyramid glows and we realise what it is a prism. the laser beam now captive in the prism, ethan carefully moves it out of the centre of the ventilator shaft and directs it toward another prism, clearing a path through the shaft.}
